Subject: [PATCH] net: hns3: format the output of the MAC address
Patch-mainline: Not yet, from openEuler
References: bsn#22
openEuler-commit: 07fb738eac84ae9feb10104628b72cf54d6b5d4f

mainline inclusion
from mainline-master
commit 4f331fda35f1
category: feature
bugzilla: https://gitee.com/openeuler/kernel/issues/I4M1HB
